lines.text: I dreamed of steaks bigger and prettier than them once.
I don't know. Just when I was about to eat them, I dreamed the dentist came in and pulled out all my teeth.
Tex, do you realize that it's nearly 6 o'clock?
Gee is it that late, honey? McCracken, are you a union man?
Union? No, but I'm an Elk.
Don't worry, boss. We won't quit til the job's finished!
